!! Lists

!!! Bullet Lists

* First item
* Second item
** Nested item 2.1
** Nested item 2.2
*** Deeply nested 2.2.1
* Third item

!!! Numbered Lists

# First numbered
# Second numbered
## Nested 2.1
## Nested 2.2
# Third numbered

!!! Definition Lists

; Term 1
: Definition for term 1
; Term 2
: Definition for term 2
: Another definition for term 2
; Complex Term
: This definition has ''bold'' and //italic// text

!!! Mixed Lists

* Bullet item
*# Numbered under bullet
*# Another numbered
*#* Bullet under numbered
* Back to bullet
*; Term in list
*: Definition in list

