!! Typed Blocks

$$$text/vnd.tiddlywiki
This content is parsed as //wikitext//.
It supports ''all'' the usual formatting.
$$$

$$$text/plain
This is plain text.
No formatting is applied.
$$$

$$$application/javascript
// This is treated as JavaScript
const x = 42;
$$$

$$$text/css
.example { color: red; }
$$$

