!! Special Characters

!!! Escape Character

The tilde escapes: ~WikiWord, ~http://example.com, ~<<macro>>.

!!! HTML Entities

&amp; &lt; &gt; &quot; &copy; &reg; &trade;

&mdash; &ndash; &hellip; &nbsp;

&#65; &#x41; (Both are 'A')

!!! Dashes

En dash -- and em dash --- in text.

!!! Hard Line Break

First line"""
Second line after hard break.

