!! Pragmas Summary

```
\define name(params) ... \end
\procedure name(params) ... \end
\function name(params) [filter]
\widget $name(params) ... \end
\rules only|except rulename...
\import [filter]
\parameters (name:default,...)
\whitespace trim|notrim
```

